caption.text:
sometimes we argue, then i cross the line, i get loud, then comes the silence, it feels like we don't wanna look at each other anymore. and comes the cold, feels like i'm freezing that i can't move, thinking of what i've done, regreting it without a chance to take it back. feeling terrible knowing the fact that i hurt you, many times,

sometimes we laugh, so hard that we cry a little, too hard until our belly hurts. having no idea how to stop, then i feel like i don't really wanna stop. i feel happy either to look at your face smiling or laughing. i want to feel more, but i'm afraid i can't right at the moment.

well that's relationship, no? we have our good times, while in the other hand we can't have it forever. nothing's everlasting, right? and i ain't god to keep you happy all the time.

but i'm gonna tell you. that i want you? no, nope, not only 'want' can express it, but i need you. i'm not just in love with you. but i love you, down from the deepest heart of mine, nevertheless i'm not sure where it is.
